description._content: Description: View of Tristan Island from the Eastward. Location: Tristan Da Cunha Date: 1927 Description: Inaccessible Island. View from ship approaching from Tristan Island. Location: Inaccessible Island, Tristan Da Cunha Date: 1927 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/777 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
